CALLING ALL 8th GRADE FAMILIES OF 42 üó£üó£!!
During this time the 8th Grade Team & Administrators will honor scholars for their hard work and dedication throughout the school year, and especially during this unprecedented time. Parents can expect to RETURN technology devices and receive class budget reimbursements and promotion/summer school information.
Students can expect to receive graduation pictures (if purchased on or before March 4th), as well as Class of 2020 paraphernalia.
Parents and students are required to stay inside their vehicles. Parents are required to enter the school site on N. Rocheblave Street to line up to retrieve trinkets, and exit on N.Tonti ONLY, and NO pictures will be taken.
